The paper deals with dialog management and natural language understanding, which are core topics in computational linguistics (cs.CL). The proposed structured annotation scheme and resulting corpus are expected to help machines understand the intention of natural language, which is a key aspect of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of neural paraphrasing systems, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.NE).
